      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>We formulated AG1 Next Gen to support your health with advanced nutrition in every scoop.* It's a match if you:</p><ul><li>Want an easy way to support your daily nutrition</li><li>Are juggling a busy life and need nutrition that keeps up</li><li>Care about improving gut health and digestion</li><li>Are getting back into fitness and want to support your energy levels</li><li>Are on GLP-1s and want additional nutritional support</li></ul>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Button"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_label",
      "label": "Button Label",
      "default": "Get Started"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "button_link",
      "label": "Button Link"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_arrow",
      "label": "Show Arrow Icon",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Image Settings"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
